    y<rsub|n-1>*<around|(|1/i*r|)>*t<rsup|n>/n!=<around|(|\<pi\>*r/2|)><rsup|1/2>*<around*|[|e<rsup|i*<around|(|r<rsup|2>-J<rsub|n-1/2><around|(|r|)>|)>>*t<rsup|n>/n!+i<rsup|n>*J<rsub|1/2-n><around|(|r|)>*t<rsup|n>/n!|]>
